        <h2>Idlenet (WIP)</h2>
        <p><i>Idlenet</i> is an incremental game that is currently in-development. It's about managing a growing network, is set in an alternate present, and will most definitely not be accurate. I consider it my first &quot;proper&quot; game, made with Love2D in Lua. Heavily inspired by the games <i>Kittens Game</i>, <i>Bitburner</i>, <i>Trimps</i>, <i>Your Chronicle</i>, <i>Orb of Creation</i>, and <i>Idling to Rule the Gods</i>. It'll be released on Windows and MacOS through itch.io and Steam. The game's source will also &quot;soon&quot; be available on Github.</p>
    </div>
